  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK171">
<l>naṭuviṉṟi naṉporuḷ veḵkiṟ kuṭipoṉṟik</l>
<l>kuṟṟamu māṅkē tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a man departing from equity covet the property (of others), at that very time will his family be destroyed and guilt be incurred.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
